= SDL_HINT_VIDEO_X11_XINERAMA =
A hint that specifies whether the X11 Xinerama extension should be used.




== Values ==
{|
|0
|disable Xinerama
|-
|1
|enable Xinerama
|}


== Default ==
By default SDL will use Xinerama if it is available.



